for instance, depending
on the algorithm being

00:30:14.680 --> 00:30:16.930
used for ranked choice voting.

00:30:16.930 --> 00:30:21.580
Vote for your
sincere intentions,

00:30:21.580 --> 00:30:24.580
not some strategized,
clever hacking

00:30:24.580 --> 00:30:28.540
of that, of whatever the
specific algorithm is.

00:30:28.540 --> 00:30:31.540
So I guess the issue
that I have in general,

00:30:31.540 --> 00:30:33.340
having followed
politics for a while

00:30:33.340 --> 00:30:37.600
and been very frustrated with
how dysfunctional government

00:30:37.600 --> 00:30:40.180
and electoral processes are and
all that, and the unfairness

00:30:40.180 --> 00:30:42.596
