underneath it all, this very

00:30:49.900 --> 00:30:52.360
human, subjective problem.

00:30:52.360 --> 00:30:55.930
And at the other
end of the spectrum

00:30:55.930 --> 00:31:01.720
is objective ways of approaching
it, like you're framing here.

00:31:01.720 --> 00:31:05.320
Just have an algorithm, which
is blind to these various

00:31:05.320 --> 00:31:06.790
subjective factors.

00:31:06.790 --> 00:31:09.820
But then at the end of
the day, as you point out,

00:31:09.820 --> 00:31:14.470
voters and politicians are going
to know about the underlying

00:31:14.470 --> 00:31:19.990
