result even if it's not really

00:31:37.780 --> 00:31:40.250
borne out in the majority of
the population, for instance.

00:31:40.250 --> 00:31:43.600
So this is just a
commentary about,

00:31:43.600 --> 00:31:46.330
even with all these objective
measures, there's always

00:31:46.330 --> 00:31:51.291
